  "instructions": [
    "Combine shrimp, fish sauce, lime juice, and rice vinegar in a bowl. Let it marinate for at least 10 minutes.",
    "Heat a pan over medium heat. Add the marinated shrimp mixture and cook until the shrimp are pink.",
    "In a separate pan, toast the peanuts over low heat until fragrant.",
    "In a large pandan leaf, spread a tablespoon of sweetened condensed milk.",
    "Add the cooked shrimp mixture on top of the milk.",
    "Sprinkle toasted peanuts and fresh cilantro over the shrimp.",
    "Fold the pandan leaf to enclose the filling.",
